Title: Diatoms Diatoms Anti pimple Powder(50 g)
Description: Diatoms is made from tiny fossilized water plants. Diatoms is a naturally occurring Siliceous sedimentary mineral compound from microscopic skeletal remains of unicellular algae like plants called diatoms. These plants have been part of the earth’s ecology since prehistoric times. It is believed that 30 million years ago the diatoms built up into deep, chalky deposits of diatomite. Diatoms is 100 % natural and organic product. It has high absorption powder and cation exchange capacity. When applied on pimples it absorbs all the sebaceous liquid from pimple and makes it dry and gives fast relief from pimples.Direction for useTake little powder in hand and mix filtered water till a paste is form, apply this paste on the pimple and let it dry. Use 3-4 times in a day. If redness occurs for long time discontinue use and apply moisturizer. First apply little paste on your hand and check its suitability to your skin. People with sensitive skin need to check it prior to application. PrecautionsDo not inhale and avoid contact with eyes as dust may give irritation in nose and eyes. Wash with plenty of water if accidently powder goes in eyes and nose. Do not keep bottle open, close the lid immediately after use. Store in a dry place.
